30:44.540 --> 30:44.930
Bom dia

30:44.930 --> 30:45.780
Bom dia, Irmã Cai

30:45.780 --> 30:46.890
Já levantaram todos

30:48.130 --> 30:49.020
Essa juventude

30:49.210 --> 30:50.370
